  "key": "C major",
  "genre": [
    "Alternative",
    "Indie"
  ],
  "difficultyLevel": 3,
  "lyrics": "Yeah, I'm thinkin' about it You know I'm dreamin' about it You know I'm workin' about it You know it's all about it I know it all, it gets harder And I've come this far to give it up for what I've done I've been runnin' out of danger In danger from lovin' me I'm in danger from bein' me In danger, I'm no stranger Do I know myself when I look you down in the eyes? When I see you, I wanna be clear I wanna be better, I wanna be everything Are you me? Baby, I wanna be, I wanna be fair I wanna stand tall, I wanna be more than just, just enough A number of sins doesn't equal a song, just Try and tell you, baby, I'm a little old You were in your mind and spirit, but you were there for me Is that how we make eternity? Is that how we come together? Can't live one another, nobody cares No, we aren't bein' out of line You better know that it takes more to be more to be there You better know that it takes more to be more to be there I gotta breathe when you're on fire Touchin' me there Yeah, I gotta know you're comin' home Gotta know, is it just another time and now? Fallin' out of place, fallin' into place Same reaction, lost it, out of space Asinine flyin' in a nautical wave Gettin' high and you thought that you wouldn't behave Break your face down with astamine Demon's inside, man, we're all the same Don't be lookin' at me, don't be lookin' at me When your day comes to an end Remember, it's all just a different kind of blue When you're blue, when you're high All in mind, just left behind You knew, you flew, you said goodbye Tonight, my son, you and me Are you here, are you feelin' Have you covered, lost it all, it's dead Come back home again Come back home and see all Lost and regretted, timeline in a mess Lost and regrets, it's all an affair Don't know why I even took so many years To think about a dream that was a loss And every kid who came could come around Fuck it all, that's what I said I'm sayin' make it, before you are years away Baby, do you feel it Baby, I know you love it Take it away, away Take it away, away",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 29.719999313354492,
      "text": "Yeah, I'm thinkin' about it You know I'm dreamin' about it",
      "start": 23.600000381469727
    },
    {
      "end": 37.20000076293945,
      "text": "You know I'm workin' about it You know it's all about it",
      "start": 29.719999313354492
    },
    {
      "end": 47.79999923706055,
      "text": "I know it all, it gets harder And I've come this far to give it up for what I've done",
      "start": 37.20000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 54.79999923706055,
      "text": "I've been runnin' out of danger In danger from lovin' me",
      "start": 47.79999923706055
    },
    {
      "end": 62.540000915527344,
      "text": "I'm in danger from bein' me In danger, I'm no stranger",
      "start": 55.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 66.95999908447266,
      "text": "Do I know myself when I look you down in the eyes?",
      "start": 62.560001373291016
    },
    {
      "end": 75.33999633789062,
      "text": "When I see you, I wanna be clear I wanna be better, I wanna be everything",
      "start": 67.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 78.05999755859375,
      "text": "Are you me?",
      "start": 76.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 91.33999633789062,
      "text": "Baby, I wanna be, I wanna be fair I wanna stand tall, I wanna be more than just, just enough",
      "start": 79.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 99.23999786376953,
      "text": "A number of sins doesn't equal a song, just Try and tell you, baby, I'm a little old",
      "start": 91.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 104.08000183105469,
      "text": "You were in your mind and spirit, but you were there for me",
      "start": 99.23999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 110.22000122070312,
      "text": "Is that how we make eternity? Is that how we come together?",
      "start": 104.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 118.27999877929688,
      "text": "Can't live one another, nobody cares No, we aren't bein' out of line",
      "start": 110.80000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 123.44000244140625,
      "text": "You better know that it takes more to be more to be there",
      "start": 118.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 125.76000213623047,
      "text": "You better know that it takes more to be more to be there",
      "start": 123.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 139.6199951171875,
      "text": "I gotta breathe when you're on fire Touchin' me there",
      "start": 128.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 148.13999938964844,
      "text": "Yeah, I gotta know you're comin' home Gotta know, is it just another time and now?",
      "start": 139.6199951171875
    },
    {
      "end": 154.66000366210938,
      "text": "Fallin' out of place, fallin' into place Same reaction, lost it, out of space",
      "start": 148.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 162.10000610351562,
      "text": "Asinine flyin' in a nautical wave Gettin' high and you thought that you wouldn't behave",
      "start": 154.8800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 169.36000061035156,
      "text": "Break your face down with astamine Demon's inside, man, we're all the same",
      "start": 162.10000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 177.94000244140625,
      "text": "Don't be lookin' at me, don't be lookin' at me When your day comes to an end",
      "start": 169.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 187.16000366210938,
      "text": "Remember, it's all just a different kind of blue When you're blue, when you're high",
      "start": 180.60000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 199.16000366210938,
      "text": "All in mind, just left behind You knew, you flew, you said goodbye",
      "start": 188.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 210.3000030517578,
      "text": "Tonight, my son, you and me Are you here, are you feelin'",
      "start": 200.17999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 215.3800048828125,
      "text": "Have you covered, lost it all, it's dead",
      "start": 210.3000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 224.3000030517578,
      "text": "Come back home again Come back home and see all",
      "start": 217.4199981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 232.16000366210938,
      "text": "Lost and regretted, timeline in a mess Lost and regrets, it's all an affair",
      "start": 225
    },
    {
      "end": 237.55999755859375,
      "text": "Don't know why I even took so many years To think about a dream that was a loss",
      "start": 232.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 243.4199981689453,
      "text": "And every kid who came could come around Fuck it all, that's what I said",
      "start": 237.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 250.94000244140625,
      "text": "I'm sayin' make it, before you are years away Baby, do you feel it",
      "start": 243.6199951171875
    },
    {
      "end": 255.55999755859375,
      "text": "Baby, I know you love it",
      "start": 251.89999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 262.9800109863281,
      "text": "Take it away, away",
      "start": 258.5
    },
    {
      "end": 293.9800109863281,
      "text": "Take it away, away",
      "start": 288.7799987792969
    }
  ],
